node.text:
Happy 100th Birthday @iris.apfel 
100  years of eye catching style…through big round glasses of course‼️ 
100 years ago this Legend was born , so I thought I would look back to see what the world was like that produced such an Icon.  It was the 1920’s, the period we portray in @chicagomusical In photo # 2. Iris came to my opening night and naturally she stole the show‼️ The year Iris was born Jazz and dance clubs were all the rage, and the world was just emerging from a pandemic, known as the Spanish Flu.  Hats and gloves were de rigueur, alcohol was prohibited, and women finally won the right to vote that year‼️Iris and the automobile industry were both born in the same year‼️
And  for 100 years Iris has been taking it all in, and seeing the world through her lens has endlessly influenced and fascinated the world‼️
 I think her vitality and youth comes from her endless fascination with life.. the other day I told Iris I was going to call her back later and she said , “you can always call me anytime except tonight I’m going to bed early because I was up all night last night shooting a music video with a rapper.” That’s Iris at 100‼️Gurl, we all hope to be like you when we grow up, .. young at heart forever‼️And we ALL love you very much✨I can’t wait to celebrate with you‼️❤️🎉
